The '''''Satna-chakka''''' was a [[Myneyrsh]] bond of peace used during meetings between two groups who in other situations would be violent to one another. The Myneyrsh used this when [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] were traveling the forests of [[Wayland/Legends|Wayland]] trying to destroy [[Mount Tantiss/Legends|Mount Tantiss]].

The bond of peace consisted of a killed bird.

